294
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:57,720
What do you think?

295
00:12:58,320 --> 00:12:59,870
Of course nothing happened.

296
00:12:59,870 --> 00:13:00,870
If something had happened,

297
00:13:00,870 --> 00:13:02,000
you would have said bad things about him.

298
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:02,790
I know Zhao Hengzhi

299
00:13:02,790 --> 00:13:03,750
very well.

300
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:05,120
He's not interested in women.

301
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:06,320
Did he reject you?

302
00:13:10,010 --> 00:13:11,480
If you're angry about this,

303
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:12,510
there's no need.

304
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:15,630
What about you?

305
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:16,270
Me?

306
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:18,200
Are you interested in women?

307
00:13:18,670 --> 00:13:19,750
I'm married.

308
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:20,600
My wife is

309
00:13:20,790 --> 00:13:22,510
one of the two women

310
00:13:22,630 --> 00:13:23,480
who came to your shop

311
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:24,150
this after—

312
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,400
One of those two women

313
00:13:29,010 --> 00:13:30,320
is also a demon.

314
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:32,210
As for the other one,

315
00:13:32,550 --> 00:13:33,550
I couldn't tell.

316
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:37,600
You look like a normal human.

317
00:13:38,270 --> 00:13:40,270
Why are you hanging out with demons?

318
00:13:46,550 --> 00:13:47,410
Are you scared?

319
00:13:50,670 --> 00:13:51,360
I got it!

320
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:53,720
You're Ms. River Snail,

321
00:13:53,720 --> 00:13:54,150
right?

322
00:13:56,030 --> 00:13:57,230
You are a hardworking

323
00:13:57,670 --> 00:13:59,240
and kind good demon.

324
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:01,240
Every Chinese knows you.

325
00:14:01,670 --> 00:14:03,360
You helped the poor farmer,

326
00:14:04,090 --> 00:14:05,910
and even washed his clothes
and cooked for him,

327
00:14:05,910 --> 00:14:06,310
right?

328
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:10,630
Then why am I here now?

329
00:14:11,150 --> 00:14:11,750
Aren't...

330
00:14:11,910 --> 00:14:13,550
Aren't you immortal?

331
00:14:13,870 --> 00:14:15,080
But your husband...

332
00:14:16,550 --> 00:14:17,950
He was a mortal after all.

333
00:14:18,510 --> 00:14:19,270
I assume

334
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:21,620
he's been dead for many years.

335
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:25,410
You must be very lonely.

336
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:32,150
Actually,

337
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:34,550
it's okay to find another man.

338
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:36,250
But Zhao Hengzhi...

339
00:14:36,390 --> 00:14:37,670
He's not suitable.

340
00:14:42,870 --> 00:14:43,750
Who is he to you?

341
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:45,900
Who are you to meddle here?

342
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:47,400
What if he is willing?

343
00:14:48,070 --> 00:14:49,120
The wife you married

344
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:50,380
isn't a mortal either.

345
00:14:50,870 --> 00:14:52,480
Why is it okay for you but not for him?

346
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:53,360
What's the logic in that?

347
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:54,840
He didn't say it was okay.

348
00:14:55,480 --> 00:14:56,750
From last night until now,

349
00:14:56,750 --> 00:14:58,030
he hasn't answered his phone.

350
00:14:58,030 --> 00:14:59,510
You must have hidden him away,

351
00:14:59,510 --> 00:14:59,960
right?

352
00:15:00,670 --> 00:15:01,530
How about this?

353
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:02,860
Just take me to see him.

354
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:03,730
If he tells me

355
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:05,200
he wants to be with you,

356
00:15:05,200 --> 00:15:06,080
as his friend,

357
00:15:06,100 --> 00:15:07,500
I won't say another word.

358
00:15:08,030 --> 00:15:09,120
On your wedding day,

359
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:10,920
I'll give you a big red envelope.

360
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,000
But right now,

361
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:13,240
I can't find him anywhere.

362
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:14,030
There's no trace of him,

363
00:15:14,030 --> 00:15:14,840
dead or alive.

364
00:15:15,030 --> 00:15:16,830
I really have to call the police.

365
00:15:34,840 --> 00:15:35,670
Follow me.

366
00:16:19,470 --> 00:16:20,180
He's over there.

